FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our Ethereum transaction finder
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app helps you discover and track new Ethereum transactions in real-time, providing detailed insights and analytics for blockchain enthusiasts and developers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How up-to-date is the transaction data?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We sync with the Ethereum blockchain in real-time, ensuring that you see new transactions as soon as they are confirmed on the network.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I set alerts for specific types of transactions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, you can customize alerts based on various parameters such as wallet addresses, contract interactions, or transaction values to stay informed about activities that matter to you.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is this app suitable for both beginners and experienced users?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! We've designed the interface to be intuitive for newcomers while offering advanced features and data analysis tools for experienced blockchain users and developers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How secure is my data when using this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We prioritize user privacy and security. The app only accesses publicly available blockchain data and doesn't require you to input any sensitive information or private keys.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: EthScan is a user-friendly app designed to help you discover and track new Ethereum transactions in real-time. It provides a seamless way to monitor the Ethereum blockchain for the latest activity.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: EthScan connects directly to the Ethereum network, constantly scanning for new transactions. When a new transaction is detected, it's instantly displayed in the app, allowing you to view details such as sender, recipient, amount, and transaction hash.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I set up alerts for specific addresses or transaction types?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes! EthScan allows you to set up custom alerts for specific Ethereum addresses or transaction types. You'll receive instant notifications when transactions matching your criteria are detected, helping you stay on top of important blockchain activity.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is EthScan suitable for both beginners and experienced users?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! EthScan is designed with an intuitive interface that's easy for beginners to navigate, while also offering advanced features for experienced users. Whether you're new to Ethereum or a seasoned blockchain enthusiast, EthScan has the tools you need to track transactions effectively.
